690
00:34:50,900 --> 00:34:52,540
When you decided to set a trap

691
00:34:52,900 --> 00:34:54,260
and use my mother

692
00:34:54,940 --> 00:34:57,660
against my entire family,

693
00:34:59,140 --> 00:35:01,540
