784
00:41:40,820 --> 00:41:41,900
What grievance do you have?

785
00:41:42,160 --> 00:41:45,220
(Law of Heaven, Fair and Impartial)
My family's execution today

786
00:41:45,500 --> 00:41:48,020
is because there's a secret passage
in our house

787
00:41:48,380 --> 00:41:51,580
leading to Pei Dafu's residence.

788
00:41:52,020 --> 00:41:55,300
I purchased this house three years ago

789
00:41:55,460 --> 00:41:59,420
from Duke Shunping.

790
00:41:59,580 --> 00:42:01,660
He dug the secret passage.

791
00:42:01,660 --> 00:42:04,940
It has nothing to do with my family.

792
00:42:05,100 --> 00:42:07,300
Today, if the innocent are killed,

793
00:42:07,500 --> 00:42:09,540
