794
00:42:09,700 --> 00:42:12,380
- The heavens can't tolerate it.
- It's too unfair.

795
00:42:12,380 --> 00:42:13,660
Let's see how it'll be handled.

796
00:42:13,660 --> 00:42:14,500
Yes.

797
00:42:35,340 --> 00:42:36,220
Zhuang Shiyang,

798
00:42:38,340 --> 00:42:41,180
there's solid evidence for this case.

799
00:42:41,540 --> 00:42:45,020
Besides, Duke Shunping
has been missing for days.

800
00:42:45,500 --> 00:42:47,420
The so-called grievance you speak of

801
00:42:47,620 --> 00:42:48,780
can't be verified.

802
00:42:49,340 --> 00:42:50,180
You should

803
00:42:50,980 --> 00:42:52,300
accept your fate.

804
00:42:53,220 --> 00:42:54,660
